# 🍕 Responsive Pizza Website  

A fully responsive pizza ordering website built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, featuring dynamic animations, a
mobile-friendly menu, and interactive product displays powered by **Swiper.js** and **ScrollReveal**.    
A fully responsive pizza ordering website with complete cart and checkout functionality.

---  

### **Libraries**  
| Library | Purpose | Files Used |  
|---------|---------|------------|  
| [Swiper.js](https://swiperjs.com/) | Carousel for popular pizzas | `swiper-bundle.min.js`, `swiper-bundle.min.css`  
| [ScrollReveal](https://scrollrevealjs.org/) | Animate elements on scroll | `scrollreveal.min.js` |  
| [RemixIcon](https://remixicon.com/) | Icons (menu, cart, etc.) | CDN link |  

### **Fonts**  
- **Google Fonts**: `Montserrat` (body), `Carter One` (titles).  

---

A fully responsive pizza ordering website with complete cart and checkout functionality.

## Features

- **Responsive Design**: Works on all devices
- **Interactive Menu**: Filter by category (Vegetarian, Meat, Premium)
- **Shopping Cart**: Add/remove items, adjust quantities
- **Checkout System**: Order form with validation
- **Order Confirmation**: Detailed confirmation message
- **Modern UI**: Attractive design with animations
- **Swiper-Powered Carousel**: Smooth, touch-enabled slides for popular pizzas using `swiper-bundle.min.js` 
+ `swiper-bundle.min.css`.  
- **ScrollReveal Animations**: Staggered element reveals on scroll.  
- **Mobile-First Navigation**: Toggleable menu with CSS transitions.  
- **Dynamic Product Cards**: Hover effects and price display.  
- **Sticky Header**: Shadow effect on scroll via JavaScript.  

---

## Technologies

- Swiper.js (for sliders)
- ScrollReveal (for animations)
- Remix Icon (for icons)
- **HTML5**: Semantic structure (`<section>`, `<article>`).  
- **CSS3**: Flexbox, Grid, Variables (`:root`), `@media` queries.  
- **JavaScript**: DOM manipulation, event listeners. 

